{"tid":954341,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"清河邨男子墮樓亡　鄰居聞大嗌聲報警","createTime":"2018-12-24T13:48:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T14:42:22.000Z","uid":160807,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ac1e9f24cc9936e1580a49c997e9860d7fed9992","tid":954341,"uid":160807,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T13:48:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181224/photo/bkn-20181224122117531-1224_00822_001_01b.jpg?20181224140226\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181224%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20181224122117531-1224_00822_001_01b.jpg%3F20181224140226&h=8a55a2e0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n上水清河邨清澤樓一單位，今早(24日)11時51分，一名中年男子突然爬出窗外，然後大叫一聲後跳下，倒臥在平台上，街坊聞聲發現報警。救護及消防員到場，證實男子已傷重死亡，警方正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181224/bkn-20181224122117531-1224_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20181224%2Fbkn-20181224122117531-1224_00822_001.html&d=SgZWlur5bQtibB4g4sFBT%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=f0fda1c2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20181224/bkn-20181224122117531-1224_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"62dee8dbd6d17aeba9e8a387ecf3f8502ad17b70","tid":954341,"uid":107364,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T13:48:46.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7cca7fdd2b1eaa2e7873863b60ea0ac3ef3bedb9","tid":954341,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-24T14:42:22.000Z","msg":"人在遠方蟬沒有和唱........"}]}